metadata.name: #1 Modern Times
metadata.description:
#1 Modern Times is a tribute to the Charlie Chaplin film "Modern Times". Inspired by the french version movie poster.

Poost Factory is an "Entreprise critique" created by RAPHMAU. Business & Art project.

A company with a Poo as a logo who wants to create a unicorn by selling the best quality Foods & Goods.

Poost wants to highlight a value inversion when the big brands sell crap sold by Magnificent branding.

RAPHMAU is dedicated to **create IRL and IVL Poost Factory.**

[website](http://www.poostfactory.com) || [twitter](http://www.twitter.com/poostFactory)
